---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import FooterNL from '../../../components/FooterNL.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Ultimo | zomeren.studio"
  description="Ultimo webdesign case study by Marco van Zomeren for WADM."
  lang="nl"
  enPath="/projects/ultimo/"
  nlPath="/nl/projects/ultimo/"
  ogImage="https://zomeren.studio/assets/images/projects/ultimo/1-ultimo-design-by-wadm.webp"
  bodyClass="project-page"
  schema={`{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"CreativeWork","name":"Ultimo | zomeren.studio","description":"Ultimo webdesign case study by Marco van Zomeren for WADM.","url":"https://zomeren.studio/nl/projects/ultimo/","inLanguage":"nl-NL","isPartOf":{"@type":"WebSite","name":"zomeren.studio","url":"https://zomeren.studio/"}}`}
>
  <Header enHref="/projects/ultimo/" nlHref="/nl/projects/ultimo/" lang="nl" />
  <main class="pb-24 md:pb-36">
    <section data-reveal>
      <img src="/assets/images/projects/ultimo/1-ultimo-design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Ultimo cover" class="project-featured-image aspect-[16/9] w-full object-cover" />
    </section>

    <section data-reveal class="px-6 pt-14 md:px-12 md:pt-20">
      <div class="grid w-full grid-cols-1 gap-12 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-12">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <h1 class="text-[clamp(2rem,5.4vw,5.2rem)] leading-[0.97] tracking-[-0.02em]">Ultimo</h1>
          <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-6 text-[clamp(1rem,1.5vw,2rem)] leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.01em]">
            <p class="uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-black/75 dark:text-white/75">What</p>
            <p>Webdesign</p>
            <p class="uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-black/75 dark:text-white/75">Where</p>
            <p>WADM</p>
            <p class="uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-black/75 dark:text-white/75">Role</p>
            <p>Designer</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-6 lg:col-start-7">
          <p class="text-[clamp(1.3rem,2.05vw,2.8rem)] leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.012em]">
            After six years, Ultimo&rsquo;s website no longer reflected the company&rsquo;s growth and transformation. The leading cloud-based Enterprise Asset Management (EAM) software provider had expanded its reputation, client base, and reach&mdash;culminating in its 2022 acquisition by Swedish tech giant IFS. With rising competition, shifting audiences, and a need for a sharper message, the time had come for a complete digital overhaul by WADM that matched Ultimo&rsquo;s new global ambitions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section data-reveal class="px-6 pt-14 md:px-12 md:pt-20">
      <div class="space-y-6 md:space-y-8">
        <video class="w-full object-cover" autoplay muted loop playsinline>
          <source src="https://res.cloudinary.com/zomerenstudio/video/upload/v1771513240/ultimo-animaties_dbkov4.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section data-reveal class="px-6 pt-16 md:px-12 md:pt-24">
      <div class="space-y-10 md:space-y-12">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-12">
          <p class="text-[clamp(1.3rem,1.35vw,1.7rem)] uppercase leading-none tracking-[0.04em] lg:col-span-2">Design</p>
          <p class="text-[clamp(1.3rem,2.05vw,2.8rem)] leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.012em] lg:col-span-8 lg:col-start-5">
            The new IFS Ultimo website was designed to emphasize growth potential and strengthen its global presence, especially in the US and Scandinavia. The strategy combined a bold, data-driven story with a refined visual identity and an entirely new UX. The site blends clarity and interactivity through graphs, infographics, and whitepapers while building emotional connection via testimonials, case studies, and animated visuals&mdash;all structured to guide C-level decision-makers and complex DMUs through a smarter sales funnel.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-12">
          <p class="text-[clamp(1.3rem,1.35vw,1.7rem)] uppercase leading-none tracking-[0.04em] lg:col-span-2">Result</p>
          <p class="text-[clamp(1.3rem,2.05vw,2.8rem)] leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.012em] lg:col-span-8 lg:col-start-5">
            Built by WADM on Statamic CMS, the new website unites strategic clarity, technical excellence, and a strong human touch. It features micro animations, GSAP scroll effects, video showcases, multilingual support (including Swedish), and user-friendly navigation tailored to different roles. The result: a technically advanced, visually powerful, and emotionally engaging platform that&rsquo;s been met with enthusiasm across the industry and renewed pride among the 7,000 global IFS employees.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section data-reveal class="px-6 pt-14 md:px-12 md:pt-20">
      <div class="space-y-6 md:space-y-8">
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/ultimo/2-ultimo-design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Ultimo image 2" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/ultimo/3-ultimo-design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Ultimo image 3" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/ultimo/4-ultimo-design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Ultimo image 4" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/ultimo/5-ultimo-design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Ultimo image 5" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/ultimo/6-ultimo-design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Ultimo image 6" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/ultimo/7-ultimo-design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Ultimo image 7" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/ultimo/8-ultimo-design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Ultimo image 8" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/ultimo/9-ultimo-design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Ultimo image 9" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/ultimo/10-ultimo-design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Ultimo image 10" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/ultimo/11-ultimo-design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Ultimo image 11" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/ultimo/12-ultimo-design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Ultimo image 12" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/ultimo/13-ultimo-design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Ultimo image 13" class="w-full object-cover" />
        <img src="/assets/images/projects/ultimo/14-ultimo-design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Ultimo image 14" class="w-full object-cover" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section data-reveal class="px-6 pt-20 md:px-12 md:pt-24">
      <p class="mb-6 text-[clamp(1.1rem,1vw,1.4rem)] uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-black/75 dark:text-white/75">More posts</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-10">
        <article>
          <a href="/nl/projects/gearfreak/" class="block">
            <img src="/assets/images/projects/gearfreak/1_gearfreak_design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Gearfreak cover" class="aspect-[4/3] w-full object-cover" />
            <div class="mt-5 flex items-end justify-between gap-4">
              <h3 class="text-[clamp(2.1rem,2.8vw,4rem)] leading-none tracking-[-0.02em]">Gearfreak</h3>
              <p class="text-[clamp(1rem,1.1vw,1.4rem)] leading-none tracking-[-0.01em] text-black/75 dark:text-white/75">Branding</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </article>
        <article>
          <a href="/nl/projects/keller/" class="block">
            <img src="/assets/images/projects/keller/1-keller-design-by-wadm.webp" alt="Keller cover" class="aspect-[4/3] w-full object-cover" />
            <div class="mt-5 flex items-end justify-between gap-4">
              <h3 class="text-[clamp(2.1rem,2.8vw,4rem)] leading-none tracking-[-0.02em]">Keller</h3>
              <p class="text-[clamp(1rem,1.1vw,1.4rem)] leading-none tracking-[-0.01em] text-black/75 dark:text-white/75">Branding</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <FooterNL />
</BaseLayout>
